Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:11.43,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}時間銀河  夢的彼方  不管在哪都是同樣的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.76,0:22:17.52,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就像包容著一切那樣  你存在於那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.81,0:22:24.44,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}似乎伸出手來就能觸到  但是現在還是保持這樣好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.73,0:22:31.70,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}溫暖的存在  慢慢地流進我心  Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.07,0:22:37.66,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在不斷流入的時間裡  我想更加了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:44.46,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}微笑起來  讓我聆聽那吐息的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:51.39,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在無限的閃爍之中  將我找到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:57.73,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}互相吸引的天空中  就連奇蹟也是命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:23:04.36,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想成為全世界中只屬於你的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:08.24,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}等待著變成戀愛的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:13.07,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}開始轉動的MoonRise Romance
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靜下心來  斬斷迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花道的深奧之處就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將心中迷惑顯現成形
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是茜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要集中力這一點跟馬上長槍比武一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  蘇利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇利亞學姐？在哪在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷惑滿天飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以你這副狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是跟蘇利亞學姐對戰  該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟蘇利亞學姐  對戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇利亞學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇利亞  學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}姐…姐…姐…姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜？茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要拿起槍對峙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算對手是蘇蘇蘇…蘇利亞學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也也也…也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,病得太重了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:03:01.03,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(580,265)}{\K115}在風車之下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這也能算騎士嗎  龍造寺茜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這  這外套是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍造寺也來避雨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇  蘇利亞學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會在這種地方遇到你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想想…想不到學姐您竟然也也也…在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點  茜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要端莊地做個自然的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣晴朗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  預告不靠譜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我連內衣都濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍造寺你也脫了怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著濕衣服會感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我身體強健沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不是說學姐你身體不強健
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你還逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說極寒之地的士兵們會將死馬的肚子割開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將手放進去以禦寒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜這裡沒有死馬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能將就用我的身體來給你取暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇利亞學姐的溫暖…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆就這樣將身子交給她算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像起風了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陽光也漏下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  看來快能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  事到如今就穿著濕衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍造寺  上來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都什麼情況了還客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再往右邊一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  太激烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍造寺？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,襪…襪子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒派上用場…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼責怪自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找找看或許能找到什麼能穿的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  紫苑？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貴弘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美櫻…看來是穿著的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  你可以幫我拉櫻牠們回馬廄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貴弘  你手上的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自古以來  人們都會利用風力磨小麥粉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以會喜歡風車
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為它是支撐著人們生活的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:09:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說戰爭時期還能當做瞭望台來用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代替衣服的東西還真難找到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試試這個好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  可  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像從繪畫中走出來一樣的美麗背影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個背承受著學園第一的重責啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍造寺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍造寺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  能幫我拉一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這  這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要勒進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  那麼我拉另一邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  要是拉那邊的話繩結會碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪啊  那麼拉這邊呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那拉這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  那裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然勉強算是遮住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣有點難動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲奧娜  你在找東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用不著學長擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找的是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我誤會了嗎  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞  搞…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊剛才那是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不能一直這樣待著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到附近的屋子裡去應該能找到能穿的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這附近很少會有人過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,運氣好的話  就不會被人看到…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有  有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  現在開始寫生大會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你們畫完之前我可不會放你們走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(260,323)\fs18}射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(304,323)\fs18}射精
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寫  寫生大會？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是寫生？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寫生大會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要把在那的人叫過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:11:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像蘇利亞學姐你這等身份的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能以這種模樣見人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們等到他們寫生結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到他們寫生結束？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是學生在寫生而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就會結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寫生有這麼快結束嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寫生技術也有個人差異的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  再不回去的話  就不能和茜一起練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好過分  好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聲音是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請找個地方藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可哪裡有能藏身的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雕像？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然擺在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去和誰好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這真像是活著的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的觸感是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無恥之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水野  原來是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事說來話長…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出去把衣服拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這副樣子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別無選擇了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來外面的門栓落下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從窗口是出不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:15:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真夠倒霉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經這麼晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我約好了要去接個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從小陪伴我的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傷口痊癒  今天就要回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想盡快和他相見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這副慘狀…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍造寺…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是你重要的好友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定在等著學姐你過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  即使可以從這裡出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在也趕不過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騎馬過去怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…紫苑！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑的話應該來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是風車的門關著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且這副模樣出去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種堅固的風車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去也做為瞭望台使用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我想像的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鎧甲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了以防萬一  總會藏著鎧甲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐  請穿上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎  龍造寺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間可以謙讓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再幫我收攏一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  蘇利亞學姐的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管是老舊的鎧甲  但是非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水野  可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過  門的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個不能打開的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用這個打開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小麥粉？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  剛剛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是塗在身上  而是撒出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過要賭一賭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水野你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用粉塵爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓這種粉狀顆粒飛揚在空氣中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能引發爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  這是個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐  請騎上來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍造寺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女神？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑  學姐她們就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐一會就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐  為什麼連我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能把裸露的你留在那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學…學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透過鎧甲  能夠聽到學姐的心跳聲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明離學姐這麼近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為您今天不會過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來晚了  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠趕上真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇利亞學姐  朋友是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,323)\fs18}Friedrich
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷德里希
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從小時候就一直是我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然傷勢很重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天可以平安出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜  貴弘  你們看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這畫好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(311,347)\fsp2\bord1\3c080808\blur2\b0}騎士和女神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.05,0:23:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在心中沉睡的往日傷痕
